        }
    }
}
```

set_entity_movement.description:
Sets the position and rotation of an entity using two coordinates.

**Example:**
```paradox
set_entity_movement = {
    id = 123
    start = {
        x = 42
        y = 21
        z = 3
    }
    target = {
        province = 124
    }
    ratio = 0.5
    rotation = 1.2
}
```

